# Copy into your Railway FRONTEND service → Variables.
# The frontend does NOT connect to MySQL — only the Spring Boot API does.
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL must be set BEFORE build (Dockerfile bakes it into the static site).
# Use your backend public URL + /api
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://YOUR-BACKEND.up.railway.app/api
#
# After the frontend has a public URL, set on the BACKEND service:
# APP_FRONTEND_BASE_URL=https://YOUR-FRONTEND.up.railway.app
